<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - iCREAM Ice Cream Parlor</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="~/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
   
</head>
<body>

   
    <!-- Page Header Start -->
    <div class="page-header">
        <div class="container text-center">
            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p><a asp-action="Index" asp-controller="Home">Home</a> / Privacy Policy</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Page Header End -->
    <!-- Privacy Content Start -->
    <div class="container-fluid py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="privacy-container">
                <div class="privacy-header">
                    <h1>🔒 Privacy Policy</h1>
                    <p>Your privacy is important to us. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="privacy-section">
                    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
                    <p>At iCREAM Ice Cream Parlor, we collect the following types of information to provide you with the best service:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-user"></i> <strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and delivery address when you register or place an order.</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-credit-card"></i> <strong>Payment Information:</strong> Credit/debit card details for processing payments (securely encrypted).</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> <strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information about how you use our website, including pages visited and time spent.</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-cookie-bite"></i> <strong>Cookies:</strong> Small data files stored on your device to enhance your browsing experience.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="privacy-section">
                    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                    <p>We use the information we collect for the following purposes:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> To process your registration and membership payments</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> To fulfill your book orders and deliver recipes</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> To send you updates about new recipes and promotions</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> To improve our website and customer service</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> To process prize money for winning recipe submissions</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> To send participation certificates</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="info-box">
                    <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                    <h3>Your Data is Safe With Us</h3>
                    <p>We use industry-standard encryption and security measures to protect your personal and payment information. We never sell your data to third parties.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="privacy-section">
                    <h2>3. Membership & Payment Information</h2>
                    <p>When you register for a membership, we collect:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-dollar-sign"></i> Monthly Membership: $15/month - Full recipe access</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-dollar-sign"></i> Yearly Membership: $150/year - Full recipe access + 1 free recipe book</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>Your payment information is processed through secure payment gateways. We do not store full credit card details on our servers.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="privacy-section">
                    <h2>4. Recipe Submissions & Prize Money</h2>
                    <p>When you submit a recipe to our platform:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-utensils"></i> Your recipe becomes part of our community collection</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-trophy"></i> Selected recipes receive prize money (amount decided by admin)</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-certificate"></i> Winners receive a participation certificate</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-star"></i> Your name will be featured on our Home Page under "Top Recipe Winners"</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="privacy-section">
                    <h2>5. Cookies & Tracking Technologies</h2>
                    <p>We use cookies to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-cookie"></i> Remember your login status</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-cookie"></i> Keep items in your shopping cart</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-cookie"></i> Analyze website traffic and improve performance</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-cookie"></i> Personalize your experience</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>You can disable cookies in your browser settings, but some features may not work properly.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="privacy-section">
                    <h2>6. Third-Party Services</h2>
                    <p>We use trusted third-party services to enhance our website:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><i class="fab fa-cc-visa"></i> Payment Processors (Stripe/PayPal)</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Email Service Providers</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-chart-simple"></i> Analytics Services (Google Analytics)</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>These services have their own privacy policies and security measures.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="privacy-section">
                    <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
                    <p>As a registered user, you have the right to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-eye"></i> Access your personal data</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-pen"></i> Correct inaccurate information</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-trash"></i> Request deletion of your account</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-download"></i> Export your data</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-ban"></i> Opt-out of marketing communications</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>To exercise these rights, please contact us at <strong>privacy@icream.com</strong></p>
                </div>

                <div class="privacy-section">
                    <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
                    <p>Our website is not intended for children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe we have collected information from a child under 13, please contact us immediately.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="privacy-section">
                    <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                    <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page and updating the "Last Updated" date. You are advised to review this policy periodically.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="info-box">
                    <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                    <h3>Contact Us</h3>
                    <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:</p>
                    <p><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Email: privacy@icream.com</p>
                    <p><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> Phone: +012 345 67890</p>
                    <p><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> Address: 123 Ice Cream Street, New York, USA</p>
                </div>

                <div class="last-updated">
                    <p>Last Updated: June 14, 2026</p>
                    <p>© 2026 iCREAM Ice Cream Parlor. All rights reserved.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Privacy Content End -->
   
    <!-- Back to Top -->
    <a href="#" class="back-to-top"><i class="fas fa-angle-double-up"></i></a>

  <script scr="~/js/js.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>